title: Keep us Humbled
itunes:title: Keep us Humbled
description:
Today on the show it was about time the host get some humbling for "Slander the Breakfast Club" and lets just say some of the listeners definitely triggered the hosts. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another Floridian woman who was arrested in Florida for making false bomb threat after arriving late for Flight and Angela helped some listeners out with "Ask Yee" with one listener having a problem being called a fiance without being engaged.
